												<h3 class="title"><a href="http://bcconsult.co.uk/?page_id=10">Training</a></h3>
						<p>Bill Crosson is a member of REHIS and holds the Advanced Diploma in Food Hygiene and the Advanced Certificate in Applied HACCP Principles. He can assess the training requirements of your staff and arrange training for them, tailored to your specific requirements. BC Consult offers Basic and Intermediate level training in Food Hygiene and/or HACCP certificated under the REHIS scheme.</p>
<p>Training is offered in three main areas : Food Hygiene and Safety, HACCP Systems,&nbsp; Internal Auditing.</p>
